+import { NgModule } from '@angular/core';
+import { Routes, RouterModule } from '@angular/router';
+
+import { TabsPagePage } from './tabs-page.page';
+
+const routes: Routes = [
+  {
+    path: 'loky',
+    component: TabsPagePage,
+    children: [
+       {
+        path: 'option',
+        loadChildren: () => import('../../../module/page/option-page/option-page.module').then(m => m.OptionPagePageModule)
+      },
+      {
+        path: 'user',
+        loadChildren: () => import('../../../module/page/user-page/user-page.module').then(m => m.UserPagePageModule)
+      },
+      {
+        path: 'gallery',
+        loadChildren: () => import('../../../module/page/gallery-page/gallery-page.module').then(m => m.GalleryPagePageModule)
+      },
+      
+    ]
+  }
+];
+
+@NgModule({
+  imports: [RouterModule.forChild(routes)],
+  exports: [RouterModule],
+})
+export class TabsPagePageRoutingModule {}

+import { NgModule } from '@angular/core';
+import { Routes, RouterModule } from '@angular/router';
+
+import { TabsPagePage } from './tabs-page.page';
+
+const routes: Routes = [
+  {
+    path: 'loky',
+    component: TabsPagePage,
+    children: [
+      {
+        path: 'option',
+        loadChildren: () =>
+          import('../../../module/page/option-page/option-page.module').then(
+            (m) => m.OptionPagePageModule
+          ),
+      },
+      {
+        path: 'user',
+        loadChildren: () =>
+          import('../../../module/page/user-page/user-page.module').then(
+            (m) => m.UserPagePageModule
+          ),
+      },
+      {
+        path: 'gallery',
+        loadChildren: () =>
+          import('../../../module/page/gallery-page/gallery-page.module').then(
+            (m) => m.GalleryPagePageModule
+          ),
+      },
+    ],
+  },
+  {
+    path: '',
+    redirectTo: '/loky/option',
+    pathMatch: 'full',
+  },
+];
+
+@NgModule({
+  imports: [RouterModule.forChild(routes)],
+  exports: [RouterModule],
+})
+export class TabsPagePageRoutingModule {}
